# Question One
## Assign x, a, and b.
```
x <- 1.1
a <- 2.2
b <- 3.3
```
## Part a
```
z <- x^a^b
print(z)
```
## Part b
```
z <- (x^a)^b
print(z)
```
## Part c
```
z<- (3*x^3) + (2*x^2) + (13*x^3) + (2*x^2) + 1
```
